{"tid":462054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為贏取iPhone X！女大生當眾脫到全裸","createTime":"2017-11-08T08:25:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-08T09:39:00.000Z","uid":75969,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"25ba1af0bf2f8516e2c209da15601a2fa0bad9d3","tid":462054,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T08:25:01.000Z","msg":"國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n蘋果十周年紀念機iPhone X推出後，吸引大批果迷爭相購買，可說是魅力無法擋，但為了得到一台新機，在眾目睽睽下脫到全裸真的值得嗎？俄羅斯一名女大生日前被拍到，在夜店內為了得到iPhone X獎項，竟當場脫光身上衣物，事情曝光後慘遭學校退學。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/11/08/1127322-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F11%2F08%2F1127322-XXL.jpg&h=72e6597e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲圖／翻攝自《mirror》<br />\n<br />\n根據外媒報導，一名19歲的女大生葉潔雅（Yevgenya S）近日在夜店參加一個活動，只要順利獲勝者就能獲得iPhone X手機，她為了得到手機，竟當眾脫光上衣，最後在旁人慫恿下，甚至把內褲也脫了，誇張行徑讓人相當傻眼。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/11/08/1127321-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F11%2F08%2F1127321-XXL.jpg&h=05788b8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲圖／翻攝自《mirror》<br />\n<br />\n而全身一絲不掛的她也相當害羞，除了不斷用手抱胸外，還企圖抱住主持人遮羞，儘管她努力隱藏身分，但影片仍被上傳到網路上，校方人員得知後將她退學處分。據了解，葉潔雅最後也沒有贏得iPhone X，只抱了安慰獎回家。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=312757\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D312757&d=2UPFK%2FPzvf41uQ%2F%2F0eDlof%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=c31a1b93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D312757&h=e1363ee1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=312757</a>"},{"pid":"485c07786fc1394fcc0ee214ea12d376e69924a2","tid":462054,"uid":75969,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T08:25:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>葉潔雅最後也沒有贏得iPhone X，只抱了安慰獎回家。</strong></span></span><br />\n<img 